Texts.Eng: A fuel hatch. Too bad it's broken.

Texts.Chs: 将燃料转换成自由。如果它正常工作，那就是。
Texts.Eng: Converts fuel into freedom. If it were working, that is.

Texts.Chs: 也族人想想想去旅行，但是不能...
Texts.Eng: Floran wantssss to travel, but can't...

Texts.Chs: 在这种情况下我不能走太远。
Texts.Eng: I can't go too far with the fuel hatch in this condition.

Texts.Chs: 看到燃料舱口是这种情况，我的心情很沮丧。
Texts.Eng: Seeing the fuel hatch in this condition dampens my mood.

Texts.Chs: 为了探索宇宙，这个燃料舱需要修复。
Texts.Eng: This fuel hatch needs to be repaired in order to explore the universe proper.
